text: Malomukachevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Meleuzovsky Selsoviet, Meleuzovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 193 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 7 km from Meleuz, 14 km from Karan. == References == Category:Rural localities in Meleuzovsky District
title: Malomukachevo
